page_title: Azure OpenAI Service encryption of data at rest
page_description: Learn how Azure OpenAI encrypts your data when it's persisted to the cloud.
chunk_content: Rotate customer-managed keysYou can rotate a customer-managed key in Key Vault according to your compliance policies. When the key is rotated, you must update the Azure AI services resource to use the new key URI. To learn how to update the resource to use a new version of the key in the Azure portal, see Update the key version.Rotating the key doesn't trigger re-encryption of data in the resource. No further action is required from the user.
